snippet.title: Mirai Trailer Telugu | Teja Sajja | Manchu Manoj | Karthik Gattamneni | PMF | 12th Sept
snippet.description:
Presenting the most awaited #MiraiTrailer Telugu!!

#Mirai is an upcoming Indian action-adventure film starring  #TejaSajja, #ManchuManoj, Ritika Nayak & Others. Directed by Karthik Gattamneni. Produced by TG Vishwa Prasad and Krithi Prasad under People Media Factory. 

In Cinemas 12th September, 2025 Worldwide.

Cast: Super Hero Teja Sajja, Manoj Manchu, Ritika Nayak, Shriya Saran, Jayaram, Jagapathi Babu

Crew: 
Director – Karthik Gattamneni
 Producers – T.G. Vishwa Prasad, Krithi Prasad
 Written By – Karthik Gattamneni, Manibabu Karanam
 Editor – Sreekar Prasad
 Music – Gowra Hari
 Director of Photography (DOP) – Karthik Gattamneni
 Dialogues – Manibabu Karanam
 CEP – Sujith Kumar Kolli
 Production Designer – Srinagendra Tangala
 Co-Director – Anil Anand
 Associate Producer – Gautam Reddy
 Action Choreography – Pradeet Seelum (Nung), Kecha Khampakdee, Maibam Nabakanta, Real Satish, Rabin Subbu, Stunts Jaswa, Stunts Sri, Nandu, Amrit Singh, Kishore Verma
 VFX Supervisor – Ramji Dott
 Production Controller – Korrapati Venkata Ramana
 Costume Designers – Rekha Boggarapu, Lanka Santoshi (for Teja Sajja)
 Art Director – Dasireddy Srinivas (Pandu)
 Chief Associate Editor – Uthura
 VFX Co-ordinator – Rajesh Muthu Subbaiah
 Color by – Deccan Dreams, Colorist – S.B. Yugendhran
 VFX by – PMF VFX, Deccan Dreams
 VFX Head – K. Surya
 VFX Supervisors – Jagan, Kumar Nirmala Srujan
 Sound Design – Raghunath Kemisetty
 Dolby Atmos Mix – E. Radha Krishna D.F. Tech
 Lyrics – Chandrabose, KK Balaji, Manibabu Karanam
 Choreographer – Polaki Vijay
 Chief Associate Directors – Kiran Bejjanki, Uthura
 Associate Directors – Shyaam Gaikwad, Abhiram Pamarthi, Manoj Duggireddy
 Associate Directors – Pareena S. Acharya, Likhith Giri Palle, Ashok Prakhyath, Rajath Saini, Somanth Lepakshi, Vamsy Garlapti, Chirayu Paudel, Ganesh Konamarthi, Saikiran Mandapuri
 Operative/Second Unit DOP – Mentem Satheesh
 Cinematography Team – Korlapati Bapiraju, Kora Veerendra Babu, Chandu Vadde, Vinay Ananthu
 Executive Producer – Ram Reddy
 PMF Digital Marketing – Sarath Chandra
 Production Executive – Srinu Chennakesavulu
 Production Manager – Bala
 Asst EP – Kranti Datti, Vineet Sai Kota
 Makeup Chief – I. Srinivas Raju
 Stills – Jagan Setty
 Publicity Designs – Ananth Kancherla, Kabilan Chelliah
 Promos – Kalyan Surya Prakash
 Digital Marketing – Manoj Valluri, Haashtag Media
 PRO – Vamsi Shekar

Trailer theme Music: 
GowraHari 

Keys: 
VikasBadisa 
Siddharth Salur
GowraHari 

Lyrics English & Sanskrit 
GowraHari 

Vocals :
Sai Charan Bhaskaruni
Chaithu Satsangi
Harshavardhan Chavali
Siva Dinavahi
Harini Ivaturi
Sindhuja Srinivasan
Vasa Pavani
Tejaswini Nandibhatla

Children chorus :
Vagdevi
Hamsini
Pradanya

snippet.title: Do You Wanna Partner - Official Trailer | Tamannaah Bhatia, Diana Penty | Prime Video India
snippet.description:
Prime Video India Presents
Do You Wanna Partner Official Trailer
Starring Tamannaah Bhatia, Diana Penty, Jaaved Jaaferi, Nakuul Mehta, Neeraj Kabi, Shweta Tiwari, Sufi Motiwala, Rannjivay Singha, Lokesh Mittal, Indranil Sengupta, Ayesha Raza
Directed by Archit Kumar and Collin D'Cunha
Written by Nandini Gupta, Aarsh Vora and Mithun Gangopadhyay
Created by Mithun Gangopadhyay and Nishant Nayak
A Dharmatic Entertainment Production

Official Release Date September 12, 2025 on Prime Video India.

About:
Best friends Shikha and Anahita turn entrepreneurs with an exciting craft beer brand, Jugaaro, to stand out in the crowded NCR beer market. However, they face gender discrimination every step of the way. To fight for an equal place in this male dominated sector, they decide to invent a fictitious male partner to help smooth their way. Invariably, things don’t go exactly as planned. What follows are their collective adventures & misadventures in trying to build a successful start-up amidst the current boom, as the bunch of misfits band together and become a family.

Trailer mashups are often created for a movie that does not exist now or to change the genre of an existing film. The trailer mashups are not only a user generated form of digital creativity but a way to create anticipation for future releases, working in tandem with current movie trailers. Movie trailers are designed to give minimal plot detail and to create hype and anticipation. Fan made trailer mashups allow the audience to perform their own cinematic spin on current movie footage. snippet.title: गौराई गं आली | Gaurai Ga Ali |  Gauri-Ganpati Festival Special |  Savaniee Ravindrra | Marathi Song
snippet.description:
गौराई गं आली | Gaurai Ga Ali |  Gauri-Ganpati Festival Special |  Savaniee Ravindrra | Savaniee Originals | Marathi Song | Mangalagaur 

About Video

snippet.title: Madharaasi - Official Trailer | Sivakarthikeyan | Rukmini | Vidyut | A.R.Murugadoss | Anirudh
snippet.description:
Junglee Music Tamil drops the much-awaited official trailer of Madharaasi, an action-packed emotional drama written and directed by A.R. Murugadoss. Starring Sivakarthikeyan in a bold, intense role alongside the talented Rukmini Vasanth, the trailer gives a powerful glimpse into a gripping narrative filled with high-stakes moments, strong character arcs, and impactful storytelling. Backed by a compelling background score from Anirudh Ravichander, Madharaasi promises to be a high-voltage entertainer that blends mass appeal with emotional depth.

With stunning visuals, hard-hitting dialogues, and a riveting plot, the Madharaasi trailer has already begun trending among fans of Tamil action movies, Sivakarthikeyan's latest films, and AR Murugadoss' direction. Whether you're here for the sharp screenplay, Anirudh’s electrifying music, or the powerful screen presence of the leads, this is one film that’s gearing up to be a Tamil cinema blockbuster in 2025. Don’t miss out—watch the trailer now and be part of the growing excitement around #MadharaasiTrailer.

#Madharaasi Grand release worldwide on September 5th ❤‍🔥

#MadharaasiTrailer #Sivakarthikeyan #RukminiVasanth #A.R.Murugadoss #AnirudhRavichander #NewMovieTrailer #TamilFullMovie #TamilTrailer #TamilNewMovies

en.title: Madharaasi - Official Trailer | Sivakarthikeyan | Rukmini | Vidyut | A.R.Murugadoss | Anirudh
en.description:
Junglee Music Tamil drops the much-awaited official trailer of Madharaasi, an action-packed emotional drama written and directed by A.R. Murugadoss. Starring Sivakarthikeyan in a bold, intense role alongside the talented Rukmini Vasanth, the trailer gives a powerful glimpse into a gripping narrative filled with high-stakes moments, strong character arcs, and impactful storytelling. Backed by a compelling background score from Anirudh Ravichander, Madharaasi promises to be a high-voltage entertainer that blends mass appeal with emotional depth.

With stunning visuals, hard-hitting dialogues, and a riveting plot, the Madharaasi trailer has already begun trending among fans of Tamil action movies, Sivakarthikeyan's latest films, and AR Murugadoss' direction. Whether you're here for the sharp screenplay, Anirudh’s electrifying music, or the powerful screen presence of the leads, this is one film that’s gearing up to be a Tamil cinema blockbuster in 2025. Don’t miss out—watch the trailer now and be part of the growing excitement around #MadharaasiTrailer.

#Madharaasi Grand release worldwide on September 5th ❤‍🔥

snippet.title: Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba Infinity Castle  |  VS TRAILER 2
snippet.description:
Tickets are on sale now for Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba Infinity Castle coming to theatres in the US and Canada on September 12!

🎟️ BUY TICKETS NOW: https://www.demonslayer-movie.com/tickets/

Official Website: https://demonslayer-anime.com/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/demonslayer.anime/
X: https://x.com/demonslayerusa

About Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba Infinity Castle:
Tanjiro Kamado – a boy who joined an organization dedicated to hunting down demons called the Demon Slayer Corps after his younger sister Nezuko was turned into a demon. 

While growing stronger and deepening his friendships and bonds with fellow corps members, Tanjiro has battled many demons with his comrades, Zenitsu Agatsuma and Inosuke Hashibira. Along the way, his journey has led him to fight alongside the Demon Slayer Corps’ highest-ranking swordsmen, the Hashira, including Flame Hashira Kyojuro Rengoku aboard the Mugen Train, Sound Hashira Tengen Uzui within the Entertainment District, as well as Mist Hashira Muichiro Tokito and Love Hashira Mitsuri Kanroji at the Swordsmith Village.

As the Demon Slayer Corps members and Hashira engaged in a group strength training program, the Hashira Training, in preparation for the forthcoming battle against the demons, Muzan Kibutsuji appears at the Ubuyashiki Mansion. With the head of the Demon Corps in danger, Tanjiro and the Hashira rush to the headquarters but are plunged into a deep descent to a mysterious space by the hands of Muzan Kibutsuji.
The destination of where Tanjiro and Demon Slayer Corps have fallen is the demons’ stronghold – the Infinity Castle. 

And so, the battleground is set as the final battle between the Demon Slayer Corps and the demons ignites.

[ STAFF ]
Original Story: Koyoharu Gotoge (JUMP COMICS / SHUEISHA)
Director: Haruo Sotozaki
Character Design/Chief Animation Director: Akira Matsushima
Screenplay: ufotable 
Sub Character Design: Miyuki Sato, Yoko Kajiyama, Mika Kikuchi
Prop Design: Masaharu Koyama
Art Director: Koji Eto
Director of Photography/Creative Finishing Work Director: Yuichi Terao
3D Director: Kazuki Nishiwaki
Color Setting: Yuko Omae
Editing: Manabu Kamino
Music: Go Shiina, Yuki Kajiura
Chief Director: Hikaru Kondo
Animation Production: ufotable

Theme Songs: 
"A World Where the Sun Never Rises" by Aimer (SACRA MUSIC / Sony Music Labels Inc.) 
"Shine in the Cruel Night" by LiSA (SACRA MUSIC / Sony Music Labels Inc.)

[ CAST ]
Tanjiro Kamado: Natsuki Hanae
Nezuko Kamado: Akari Kito
Zenitsu Agatsuma: Hiro Shimono
Inosuke Hashibira: Yoshitsugu Matsuoka
Kanao Tsuyuri: Reina Ueda
Genya Shinazugawa: Nobuhiko Okamoto
Giyu Tomioka: Takahiro Sakurai
Tengen Uzui: Katsuyuki Konishi
Muichiro Tokito: Kengo Kawanishi
Shinobu Kocho: Saori Hayami
Mitsuri Kanroji: Kana Hanazawa
Obanai Iguro: Kenichi Suzumura
Sanemi Shinazugawa: Tomokazu Seki
Gyomei Himejima: Tomokazu Sugita
Akaza (Upper Three): Akira Ishida

X: https://x.com/demonslayerusa

About Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba Infinity Castle:
Tanjiro Kamado – a boy who joined an organization dedicated to hunting down demons called the Demon Slayer Corps after his younger sister Nezuko was turned into a demon. 

While growing stronger and deepening his friendships and bonds with fellow corps members, Tanjiro has battled many demons with his comrades, Zenitsu Agatsuma and Inosuke Hashibira. Along the way, his journey has led him to fight alongside the Demon Slayer Corps’ highest-ranking swordsmen, the Hashira, including Flame Hashira Kyojuro Rengoku aboard the Mugen Train, Sound Hashira Tengen Uzui within the Entertainment District, as well as Mist Hashira Muichiro Tokito and Love Hashira Mitsuri Kanroji at the Swordsmith Village.

As the Demon Slayer Corps members and Hashira engaged in a group strength training program, the Hashira Training, in preparation for the forthcoming battle against the demons, Muzan Kibutsuji appears at the Ubuyashiki Mansion. With the head of the Demon Corps in danger, Tanjiro and the Hashira rush to the headquarters but are plunged into a deep descent to a mysterious space by the hands of Muzan Kibutsuji.
The destination of where Tanjiro and Demon Slayer Corps have fallen is the demons’ stronghold – the Infinity Castle. 

And so, the battleground is set as the final battle between the Demon Slayer Corps and the demons ignites.

snippet.title: Baahubali: The Epic - Official Trailer (2025)
snippet.description:
Before RRR took the world by storm, master filmmaker S.S. Rajamouli redefined Indian Cinema with his two-part BAAHUBALI saga. Now, the epic tale of royalty, revenge, kings, and wars has been personally re-edited by the master himself from two films into a single unforgettable cinematic experience, with fully remastered picture and sound (and a few new surprises), so audiences can reunite to experience the euphoria the way it was intended: on the big screen, together. 

When a lost prince is rescued and raised in exile, he grows up unaware of his past. Years later, he returns to uncover the truth about his father’s murder and his mother’s imprisonment, and must rise to reclaim his place as the rightful king.

Baahubali: The Epic will be released in theaters across the U.S. October 31st.

#IGN #Movies

snippet.title: JUGNUMA Official Trailer | Manoj Bajpayee | Raam Reddy | Presented by Guneet Monga & Anurag Kashyap
snippet.description:
Jugnuma – a story where magic comes to life!

From the award-winning filmmaker Raam Reddy comes a story for the ages.

Set in the late 1980s Himalayas, Jugnuma follows Dev (Manoj Bajpayee), an orchard owner facing the eerie mystery of trees burning overnight. His search for answers uncovers buried family truths and folklore.
Shot entirely on film, this tale blends myth, dream, and reality into a timeless, poetic journey.

Jugnuma releases in theatres across India on September 12, 2025.

Writer & Director: Raam Reddy
Producers: Pratap Reddy, Sunmin Park, Raam Reddy, Juhi Agarwal
Executive Producers: Guneet Monga Kapoor, Achin Jain, J Ethan Park, Ranjan Singh & Anurag Kashyap
Co-producer: Ganesh Babu Shetty & Nancy Nisa Beso

Cast:
Manoj Bajpayee, Priyanka Bose, Deepak Dobriyal, Tillotama Shome, Hiral Sidhu, Awan Pookot

Crew:
Director of Photography: Sunil Ramkrishna Borkar
Editors: Siddharth Kapoor, Raam Reddy
Production Designer: Juhi Agarwal
Costume Designer: Sachin Lovalekar
Casting Director: Tess Joseph (CSA)
Secondary Casting Director: Gurpal Singh
Sound Designer: Nithin Lukose
Colorist: Himanshu Kamble
Visual Effects Supervisor: Varun Ramanna
Hair & Make-up Design: Abhijeet (Makeup Artist)
Hindi Dialogue Writer: Varun Grover
Storyboard Artist: Upamanyu Bhattacharyya
Marketing: Bombay Hustle
Distribution Consultant: Metamorf Films
Media Consultant: Priyanka Chandra (Mulberry Media)
Publicity Design & Visual Promotions: Warriors Ttouch
A Flip Films & Cinepolis Release
Trailer Music Composer: Nir Perlman
Trailer Music Editor: Siddharth Kapoor

✨ May Lord Ram’s blessings bring love, light, and positivity into your life.
🔔 Stay connected with us for more soulful bhakti songs and spiritual music.

#Mangli #IndravathiChauhan #SureshBobbili #KabirDas #RamBhajan #SitapathiRamchandra #BhaktiSong #DevotionalSongs #RamBhakti 

This Song is an Adaptation of Sant Kabir Das Ji’s Bhajan

Music - Suresh Bobbili

DOP - Tirupathi 
2nd Camera - Pavanmani

Art- Chetla Vijay Chendar

सुन्दरकांड” – श्री राम चरित मानस का 5 वा अध्याय/कांड है। सुन्दर कांड (Sundar Kand) को सबसे पहले रामायण में श्री वाल्मीकि जी ने संस्कृत में लिखा था। बाद में तुलसी दस जी ने जब श्री राम चरित मानस लिखी, तो सुन्दर कांड का अवधी भाषा वाला रूप हम सब के सामने आया 
सुन्दरकाण्ड में हनुमान जी का सीता माता को खोजने के लिए की गयी लंका यात्रा का सम्पूर्ण मनमोहक बखान किया गया है।
सुन्दरकांड एक ऐसा भाग है जो सिर्फ हनुमान जी की वीरता का बखान करता है । सुन्दर कांड हनुमान जी पर केंद्रित सबसे पुरानी रचना है। ऐसा माना जाता है के सुन्दरकाण्ड के पाठ से सभी मनोकामनाएं पूर्ण होती हैं ।

सुन्दर कांड के फायदे | Benefits of - Sunder Kand
 यह कहा जाता है कि चालीस सप्ताह तक लगातार जो कोई श्रद्धापूर्वक Sundarkand का पाठ करता है, तो उसके सभी मनोरथ पूरे होते हैं तथा जीवन के सभी कष्ट, दुःख, परेशानियाँ दूर हो जाती हैँ । कई ज्योतिषी भी विपरित परिस्थितियों में सुंदरकांड करने की ही सलाह देते हैं। यदि किसी व्यक्ति के जीवन में अत्यधिक परेशानियां हो तथा कोई काम नहीं बन पा रहा है, आत्मविश्वास की कमी हो तो सुंदरकांड के पाठ से शुभ फल प्राप्त होता है।

                                                    🌸 राधा अष्टमी 2025 विशेष 🌸
        आज राधा रानी जी का पावन प्रकटोत्सव है। राधा अष्टमी के इस शुभ दिन पर राधा-कृष्ण भक्ति में डूब जाइए।
       श्री राधा रानी जी के मधुर भजन, कथा और आरती सुनकर मन को अद्भुत शांति और आनंद की प्राप्ति होती है।

                                                       💐 राधा रानी जी का महत्व :
राधारानी बिना कृष्ण अधूरे हैं, और कृष्ण बिना राधा। राधा जी प्रेम, भक्ति और करुणा की प्रतिमूर्ति हैं। राधा अष्टमी के दिन व्रत, कथा व भजन का विशेष महत्व है।

snippet.title: गणेश चतुर्थी स्पेशल: Parvatichya Bala गणपती माझा नाचत आला | Ganpati Video Song | गणपतीची गाणी
snippet.description:
गणेश चतुर्थी स्पेशल 2025 🙏✨ – पार्वतीच्या बाळा (Parvatichya Bala)
🎶 सुपरहिट गणपती गाणी | भक्ति गीत | Marathi Ganpati Song

“Parvatichya Bala” हे गाणं श्री गणेशाची भक्ती, आनंद आणि उत्साहाने भरलेलं आहे. गणपती बाप्पाच्या आराधनेसाठी हे गाणं गणेश चतुर्थी, आरती, पूजाअर्चा, गणेश उत्सव आणि गणेश विसर्जन यासाठी सर्वोत्तम आहे.

Song Credits:
🎤 Singers: Suryakant Shinde
🎼 Music: Madhu Redkar
🎬 Production: Rohit Kathuria
📀 Label: © Fountain Music Company

👉 गणेश चतुर्थीच्या निमित्ताने हे गाणं मित्र-मैत्रिणी व कुटुंबासोबत Share करा आणि Subscribe 🔔 करा आणखी भक्तिगीते ऐकण्यासाठी.

✨ गणपती बाप्पा मोरया! मंगल मूर्ती मोरया! 🙏

Song Lyrics:
गणपती बाप्पा (मोरया)
मंगलमुर्ती (मोरया)
आला रे आला (गणपती आला)
आला रे आला (गणपती आला)
Ganpati Bappa (Morya)
Mangal Murti (Morya)
Aala re aala (Ganpati aala)
Aala re aala (Ganpati aala)

पार्वतीच्या बाळा, पायात वाळा
पार्वतीच्या बाळा, पायात वाळा
पुष्प हारांच्या घातलात माळा
Paarvatichya baala, paayat vaala
Paarvatichya baala, paayat vaala
Pushpa haaranchya ghatlaat maala

ताशाचा आवाज
ताशाचा आवाज तारारारा झाला र
गणपती माझा नाचत आला
Taashacha aavaaj
Taashacha aavaaj taarararaa zhaala re
Ganpati maza naachat aala

मोदक, लाडू संगतीला घेऊ
भक्ती भावाने देवाला वाहु
गणरायचे गुण गान गाऊ
डोळे भरून देवाला पाहु
(देवाला पाहु, देवाला पाहु)
(देवाला पाहु, देवाला पाहु)
Modak, ladoo sangatila gheu
Bhakti bhaavane Devala vaahu
Ganaraayache gun gaan gaau
Dole bharun Devala paahu
(Devala paahu, Devala paahu)
(Devala paahu, Devala paahu)

गाव हा सारा गरजून गेला र
गणपती माझा नाचत आला
गाव हा सारा
गणपती माझा नाचत आला
Gaav ha saara garajoon gela re
Ganpati maza naachat aala
Gaav ha saara
Ganpati maza naachat aala

वंदन माझे तुझिया पाया
धरी शिरावर कृपेची छाया
भक्ताला या दर्शन तू द्याया
देवाजी देवा हे गणराया
(देवाजी देवा हे गणराया)
(देवाजी देवा हे गणराया)
Vandan maze tujhya paaya
Dhari shiravar krupachi chhaya
Bhaktala ya darshan tu dyaaya
Devaji Deva he Ganaraaya
(Devaji Deva he Ganaraaya)
(Devaji Deva he Ganaraaya)

ताशाचा आवाज
गणपती माझा नाचत आला
(ताशाचा आवाज तारारारा झाला हो)
(गणपती माझा नाचत आला)
(ताशाचा आवाज तारारारा झाला हो)
(गणपती माझा नाचत आला)
Taashacha aavaaj
Ganpati maza naachat aala
(Taashacha aavaaj taarararaa zhaala ho)
(Ganpati maza naachat aala)
(Taashacha aavaaj taarararaa zhaala ho)
(Ganpati maza naachat aala)

फटाके उडती, चाले जयघोश
नाचाया, गाया आलाया जोश
धुंदीत झाले, ये बेहोश
मोहाचे सारे तोडुन पाश
(मोहाचे सारे तोडुन पाश)
(मोहाचे सारे तोडुन पाश)
Phatake udati, chaale jayaghosh
Naachaya, gaaya aalaya josh
Dhundit jhaale, ye behosh
Mohache saare toduun paash
(Mohache saare toduun paash)
(Mohache saare toduun paash)

मजा हि येते दर वर्षाला र
गणपती माझा नाचत आला
ताशाचा आवाज
गणपती माझा नाचत आला
(ताशाचा आवाज तारारारा झाला हो)
(गणपती माझा नाचत आला)
(ताशाचा आवाज तारारारा झाला हो)
(गणपती माझा नाचत आला)
Maja hi yete dar varshaala re
Ganpati maza naachat aala
Taashacha aavaaj
Ganpati maza naachat aala
(Taashacha aavaaj taarararaa zhaala ho)
(Ganpati maza naachat aala)
(Taashacha aavaaj taarararaa zhaala ho)
(Ganpati maza naachat aala)

पार्वतीच्या बाळा, तुझ्या पायात वाळा
पार्वतीच्या बाळा तुझ्या पायात वाळा
पुष्प हारांच्या घातलात माळा
ताशाचा आवाज तारारारा झाला र
गणपती माझा नाचत आला
Paarvatichya baala, tujhya paayat vaala
Paarvatichya baala, tujhya paayat vaala

snippet.title: Ashirwad (Official Video) - Masoom Sharma, Aamin Barodi & Raju Kandela | New Haryanvi Song 2025
snippet.description:
Ashirwad (Official Video) - Masoom Sharma, Aamin Barodi & Raju Kandela | New Haryanvi Song 2025

Raja Ji Records proudly presents "Ashirwad", a soulful and powerful Haryanvi song of 2025. Featuring standout performances by Aamin Barodi, Muskan Thakur, Amit Balyan, and Raju Kandela, this video brings emotion and storytelling together in a beautiful musical journey.

Sung by the dynamic duo Masoom Sharma and Swara Verma, with touching lyrics by Aamin Barodi and melodious music by Pinna Music, Ashirwad is sure to leave a lasting impression on every Haryanvi music lover.

snippet.title: 🙏 Jai Ganesh Deva Arti 2025 | शहनाज़ अख्तर  व प्रतीक श्रीवास्तव  | Ganpati Aarti 2025 |
snippet.description:
🌺 जय श्री गणेश 🌺

🙏 जय गणेश जय गणेश आरती | शहनाज़ अख्तर  व प्रतीक श्रीवास्तव  | Ganpati Aarti 2025 | Jai Shree Ganesh

आप सभी भक्तों के लिए प्रस्तुत है एक पावन गणेश आरती —
"जय गणेश जय गणेश" —
लोकप्रिय भजन गायिका शहनाज़ अख्तर जी और भावपूर्ण गायक प्रतीक श्रीवास्तव जी की मधुर आवाज़ में।

🎤 - Singer :- Shahnaaz Akhtar & Prateek Srivastava
https://www.instagram.com/shahnaaz_ak...
🎶 - Lyrics and Composition -Traditional
🎶 - Music Arrangment :- Prateek Shrivastava 
https://www.instagram.com/prateek_shr...
🎛️ - Recorded At :- Shahnaaz Akhtar Studio
🎛️ - Mixed And Master :- Prateek Shrivastava

Video Credit :-
💽 - Video and Editing :- Devendra Varsha Rajak 
Distribution Partner :- Vianet media 
Label & Copyrights :- Shahnaaz Akhtar 
Digital Management Partner:- Always Digi Media

🪔 गणेश चतुर्थी, भजन संध्या, आरती और पूजा के समय इस आरती को ज़रूर सुनें और अपने घर में श्री गणेश जी की कृपा प्राप्त करें।
इस भक्ति गीत को लाइक करें, कमेंट करें और अपने सभी दोस्तों व परिवार के साथ शेयर करें।
चैनल को सब्सक्राइब करें और बेल आइकन 🔔 दबाएँ ताकि हर नई आरती की सूचना तुरंत मिले।

hi.description:
🌺 जय श्री गणेश 🌺

🙏 जय गणेश जय गणेश आरती | शहनाज़ अख्तर  व प्रतीक श्रीवास्तव  | Ganpati Aarti 2025 | Jai Shree Ganesh

आप सभी भक्तों के लिए प्रस्तुत है एक पावन गणेश आरती —
"जय गणेश जय गणेश" —
लोकप्रिय भजन गायिका शहनाज़ अख्तर जी और भावपूर्ण गायक प्रतीक श्रीवास्तव जी की मधुर आवाज़ में।

🎤 - Singer :- Shahnaaz Akhtar & Prateek Srivastava
https://www.instagram.com/shahnaaz_ak...
🎶 - Lyrics and Composition -Traditional
🎶 - Music Arrangment :- Prateek Shrivastava 
https://www.instagram.com/prateek_shr...
🎛️ - Recorded At :- Shahnaaz Akhtar Studio
🎛️ - Mixed And Master :- Prateek Shrivastava

Video Credit :-
💽 - Video and Editing :- Devendra Varsha Rajak 
Distribution Partner :- Vianet media 
Label & Copyrights :- Shahnaaz Akhtar 
Digital Management Partner:- Always Digi Media

🪔 गणेश चतुर्थी, भजन संध्या, आरती और पूजा के समय इस आरती को ज़रूर सुनें और अपने घर में श्री गणेश जी की कृपा प्राप्त करें।
इस भक्ति गीत को लाइक करें, कमेंट करें और अपने सभी दोस्तों व परिवार के साथ शेयर करें।
चैनल को सब्सक्राइब करें और बेल आइकन 🔔 दबाएँ ताकि हर नई आरती की सूचना तुरंत मिले।

snippet.description:
ಶನಿವಾರ ಈ ಹಾಡು ಕೇಳಿದರೆ ಆರ್ಥಿಕ ಸಮಸ್ಯೆಗಳು ದೂರವಾಗುತ್ತವೆ | Lord Hanuman Kannada Devotional Songs

🙏 ಶನಿವಾರ ಹನುಮಂತ ಭಕ್ತಿ ಹಾಡುಗಳು | Lord Hanuman Kannada Devotional Songs 🙏

Listening to Lord Hanuman devotional songs on Saturdays is believed to remove obstacles, solve financial problems, and bring peace, health, and prosperity. This powerful Kannada Bhakti Song is dedicated to Sri Anjaneya Swamy (Hanuman).

✨ Benefits of Listening on Saturday:

Removes financial & life problems

Brings courage, confidence & strength

Protects from negative energies

Brings blessings of Lord Hanuman

🎧 Best to listen during early morning, evening prayers, or Saturday Hanuman pooja.

👉 Don’t forget to Like 👍 | Share 🔗 | Subscribe 🔔 for more Kannada Devotional Songs, Hanuman Songs, and Bhakti Padagalu.

#HanumanSongs #KannadaDevotionalSongs #SaturdayBhaktiSongs #HanumanBhakti #KannadaBhaktiSongs #HanumanChalisaKannada

snippet.title: Nesthama Iddari Telugu Lyrical Song l Pelli Pandiri l Jagapathi Babu, Raasi | S P Balu, K S Chithra
snippet.description:
Listen & Enjoy Nesthama Iddari Song with Telugu Lyrics from the Movie Pelli Pandiri, Starring Jagapathi Babu & Raasi. A Beautiful Melody Sung by S. P. Balasubrahmanyam & K. S. Chithra, with Music by Vandemataram Srinivas and Directed by Kodi Ramakrishna.

Song Details:

Song Name: Nesthama Iddari 
Singers: S. P. Balasubrahmanyam, K. S. Chithra
Lyrics: Guru Charan
Music: Vandemataram Srinivas

Movie Details:

Movie Name: Pelli Pandiri
Banner: S R S Art Movies
Producers: M.C. Sekhar, Ramesh Babu
Director: Kodi Ramakrishna
Starring: Jagapathi Babu, Raasi

Nesthama Iddari Song Telugu Lyrics:

నేస్తమా ఇద్దరి లోకం ఒకటేలేవమ్మా
అందుకే నా కన్నులతో లోకం చూడమ్మా
ఈ గుండెలోన నీ ఊపిరుంటే
ఈ కళ్ళలోన నీ కలలు ఉంటే
ఊహల రెక్కల పైన ఊరేగే దారులు ఒకటే
చూపులు ఎవరివైనా చూపించే లోకం ఒకటే 
బుగ్గ మీద వెచ్చని సిగ్గు వచ్చినప్పుడు దానిని అడుగు
ఎర్రదనం అంటే చెబుతుందీ
పెదవి కొమ్మ పూసిన పువ్వు అందమైన నీ చిరునవ్వు
తెల్లరంగు అట్టా ఉంటుందీ
నీలో నిలువున పులకలు రేగిన వేళా
నువ్వే పచ్చని పైరువు అవుతావమ్మా
దిగులు రంగే హ హ నలుపు అనుకో హ హ
ప్రేమ పొంగే హ హ పసుపు అనుకో హ
భావాలను గమనిస్తుంటే ప్రతి రంగును చూస్తున్నట్టే
చూపులు ఎవరివైనా చూపించే లోకం ఒకటే
మొదటిసారి నీ గుండెలలో తీయనైన ఆశలు రేపి ఆ కదలికే ఉదయం అనుకోమ్మా
చూడలేని ఆవేదనతో కలత చెంది అలిశావంటే సాయంత్రం అయినట్టేనమ్మా
నీలో నవ్వినా ఆశలు నా చెలివైతే నేనై
పలికిన పలుకులు నీ కూలుకైతే
ఇలవు నీవే హ హ రవిని నేనై హ హ
కలువ నీవే హ హ శశిని నేనే హ
ఒక్కరి కోసం ఒకరం అనుకుంటూ జీవిస్తుంటే
చూపులు ఎవరివైనా చూపించే లోకం ఒకటే

#NesthamaIddari #PelliPandiri #JagapathiBabu #Jagapathi #Raasi #SPBalasubrahmanyam #KSChithra #KodiRamakrishna #TeluguSongs #TeluguEvergreenSongs #TeluguHitSongs #TeluguMelodySongs #TeluguLyricalSongs #TeluguLyrics #MaaPaataMeeNota

మొదటిసారి నీ గుండెలలో తీయనైన ఆశలు రేపి ఆ కదలికే ఉదయం అనుకోమ్మా
చూడలేని ఆవేదనతో కలత చెంది అలిశావంటే సాయంత్రం అయినట్టేనమ్మా
నీలో నవ్వినా ఆశలు నా చెలివైతే నేనై
పలికిన పలుకులు నీ కూలుకైతే
ఇలవు నీవే హ హ రవిని నేనై హ హ
కలువ నీవే హ హ శశిని నేనే హ
ఒక్కరి కోసం ఒకరం అనుకుంటూ జీవిస్తుంటే
చూపులు ఎవరివైనా చూపించే లోకం ఒకటే
